---
layout: default.hbs
subject: We are processing your Hedges Direct order | Reference number ${transaction.createdfrom.tranid}
---
<span class="preheader">You can see the details of your order below.</span>
<div class="header">
  <table>
    <tr>
      <td class="align-center">
        <a href="http://www.hedgesdirect.co.uk"><img src="https://system.eu1.netsuite.com/core/media/media.nl?id=3942&c=4635725_SB1&h=f414b4be4f035671560e" height="80" alt="Hedges Direct Logo"></a>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
<table class="main">
  <tr>
    <td class="wrapper">
      <table>
      <tr>
        <td>
        <p>Dear ${entity.firstname} ${entity.lastname},</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <p>Your order, ref: ${transaction.createdfrom.tranid} is now being processed</p>
            <p>Deliveries are made within 3 to 5 working days by courier. If your order requires a pallet we may contact you regarding delivery.</p>
            <p>You will receive confirmation of the dispatch of your order but should you have any queries in the meantime please contact our service team on <b>01257 263873</b></p>
            <p><b>Need Help Planting?</b><p>
            <p>Visit our Youtube channel for helpful videos on what you'll need and how to plant, including preparing the ground and using rootgrow. Or, for a written explanation, visit our blog and advice section.</p>
            {{> button type='hedges' url=hd.blog_url title='Hedges Blog' }}
            <p>The details of your order are;</p>
            <table>
            <#list transaction.item as item><#if item_index==0>
              <thead>
                <tr><th>{item.quantity@label}</th><th>{item.itemname@label}</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              </#if>
                <tr><td>${item.quantity}</td><td>${item.description}</td></tr>
               </#list>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
<tr>
  <td>{{> bodybase_hd }}</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="footer">
  <table>
  <tr>
      <td class="align-center">
        <p>{{> socialbar_hd }}</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="align-center">
        <p>{{> visit_hd }}</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
